* <u>{{project_name_long}} with CLI</u>: Advanced users who are comfortable using {{project_name_long}} with the command-line interface (CLI) can choose to permanently set this option.
* <u>Experiments</u>: Users can experiment with RAM assignments lower than 256 MB. We encourage you to share your results.

